title: Darzi Mahalleh, Babol
data: Darzi Mahalleh (Persian: درزي محله, also Romanized as Darzī Maḩalleh)[1] is a village in Babol Kenar Rural District, Babol Kenar District, Babol County, Mazandaran Province, Iran. In the 2006 census, its population was 405 with 104 families.[2] This Babol County location article is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it.
